{"tid":1950211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港暫增35初步確診 遊泰男26日後深喉仍驗出病毒","createTime":"2020-03-30T07:46:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T10:19:35.000Z","uid":244704,"like":88,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"93f7dc62c3836af01482dc0dd69a23b61e5abb52","tid":1950211,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T07:46:32.000Z","msg":"　本港武漢肺炎疫情持續，截至昨日（29日）下午4時，本港已確診641宗。而由昨午4時至今，本港至少多35宗初步確診，當中至少21宗有外遊，其中至少6人是留學生，大部份都是英國留學生。其中1名留醫威院的33歲男，2月22日至3月1日曾到曼谷，相隔26日、即3月27日的深喉唾液檢測呈陽性。假設病人在曼谷受感染，即病毒在體內存在超過20日。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200330/X6A352OPSSFB7YN36IW37C46FI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200330%2FX6A352OPSSFB7YN36IW37C46FI%2F&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2YT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=12a7fba9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200330%2FX6A352OPSSFB7YN36IW37C46FI%2F&h=634ca18a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200330/X6A352OPSSFB7YN36IW37C46FI/</a>"},{"pid":"4bb5be32e1b99aabef2f357fc99d0ce21bd2da1e","tid":1950211,"uid":145923,"like":107,"dislike":20,"score":87,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T07:49:58.000Z","msg":"多謝外遊撚 多謝留學撚  多謝香港政府"},{"pid":"3e0ebca9ab2bb1a229c82f72656b6aac4f6c6f15","tid":1950211,"uid":51212,"like":42,"dislike":14,"score":28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T07:53:21.000Z","msg":"得35宗，無事啦可以唔洗戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55625f8878f3932bf50a4535f90c082b014a02ad","tid":1950211,"uid":217411,"like":88,"dislike":4,"score":84,"quote":{"pid":"3e0ebca9ab2bb1a229c82f72656b6aac4f6c6f15","tid":1950211,"uid":51212,"like":42,"dislike":14,"score":28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T07:53:21.000Z","msg":"得35宗，無事啦可以唔洗戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T07:54:21.000Z","msg":"你個名好襯你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/g